# Cursor Rules for iHeard.ai Shopify App

- Follow Remix/Shopify coding standards
- All new features must include unit/integration tests
- Update PROJECT_PROGRESS.md after each major task
- Document all voice-related changes in VOICE_INTEGRATION_PRD.md
- Use TypeScript for all new code
- Add docstrings/comments for all public functions
- Use Prettier and ESLint for formatting/linting
- Cross-reference backend voice API docs for integration points
- Keep SCOPE_CHANGES.md up to date for any requirement changes 